* Specify a server name defined in the dsm.sys file
SErvername {{ tsmbackup_server }}

* Specify whether to continue compressing files even if their size
* increases through the use of compression. (default: Yes)
COMPRESSAlways {{ tsmbackup_compress_always }}

* Specifies if symlinks are followed and the target is backed up (Yes)
* or if just the symbolic link is backed up (No).
*  ** Valid with the "archive" command ONLY!
ARCHSYMLinkasfile {{ tsmbackup_archive_symlink_as_file }}

* Specifies if symlinks are followed during incremental backups and if
* files should be restored to the target of the symlink. (Default: no)
*  ** Valid with the "incremental", "restore", and "retrieve" commands.
FOLlowsymbolic {{ tsmbackup_follow_symlinks }}

* Specify the default domain of files to be backed up.
{% for _directory in tsmbackup_backup_dirs %}
DOMain {{ _directory }}
{% endfor %}
